Package hotelproject.views

Class NewBookingView

java.lang.Object
hotelproject.views.View
hotelproject.views.NewBookingView
public class NewBookingView
extends View
This view aims for adding a new booking to the database. All users have access to this view. User can add a new booking by fulfilling all the selections.
